OL,3,CInsurance advice issued for those
OL,4,Caffected by storm damage
OL,6,FAn insurance claims manager is
OL,7,Foffering advice to people whose
OL,8,Fproperties have fallen victim to Storm
OL,9,FIsha.
OL,11,FGusts of up to 84mph hit Cumbria, with
OL,12,Fwidespread disruption and damage seen
OL,13,Facross the region.
OL,15,FThe south of Scotland also experienced
OL,16,Fdamage to buildings as well as
OL,17,Fcancelled rail services.
