OL,3,CInsurance advice issued for those
OL,4,Caffected by storm damage
OL,6,FStuart Torrance, an insurance claims
OL,7,Fmanager at H&H, said: "The general
OL,8,Fadvice would be the same for all
OL,9,Fparties whether they are insured or
OL,10,Fnot insured really; when it is safe to
OL,11,Fdo so, gather as much evidence as you
OL,12,Fpossibly can - take photographs of any
OL,13,Fdamage, then assess and do a tally of
OL,14,Fwhat damage we are talking about."
OL,16,FHe continued: "If it is building
OL,17,Fdamage, make sure you do a full
OL,18,Fassessment and make sure we know which
OL,19,Fbuildings are affected and the extent
OL,20,Fof the damage.
