OL,3,CInsurance advice issued for those
OL,4,Caffected by storm damage
OL,6,F"We have to see how bad the damage is
OL,7,Fand insurers have to know whether to
OL,8,Fappoint an adjuster or not.
OL,10,F"Generally in the industry we say for
OL,11,Fanything sub #5,000 they may not send
OL,12,Fan adjuster out, so it is really just
OL,13,Fgetting an estimate of the damage at
OL,14,Fthe premises."
OL,16,FHe went on to give information about
OL,17,Fwhat people should do if they're
OL,18,Funsure what the next steps are.
