OL,3,CInsurance advice issued for those
OL,4,Caffected by storm damage
OL,6,FHe said: "Secure any quotations from
OL,7,Fcontractors and then start calling
OL,8,Fcontractors straight away, don't wait
OL,9,Ffor insurers. Get people on board, get
OL,10,Fpeople instructed and get to the front
OL,11,Fof the queue."
OL,13,F"People can check their own policy
OL,14,Fdocumentation, if they know they have
OL,15,Finsured through a broker then get in
OL,16,Ftouch with them.
OL,18,F"They will certainly be on hand to
OL,19,Fadvise of the cover that a customer
OL,20,Fhas got. We always try and advise our
OL,21,Fclients of the best way forward.
